The Oregon Trail example
  The original game was created in 1971 by Don Rawitsch, Bill Heinemann, and
  Paul Dillenberger. A BASIC listing by Rawitsch was published in *Creative
  Computing*, May–June 1978. The example in
  examples/creative-computing-magazine was sourced from
  https://github.com/clintmoyer/oregon-trail and is provided there under the
  Unlicense. See its local README.md and LICENSE.

